bfillds
bcbuild r

bcremoveall
bcadd result s1 1 s2 0 s3 0 -m 1
bcadd result s1 1 s2 0 s3 1 -m 1
bcadd result s1 1 s2 1 s3 0 -m 2
bcadd result s1 1 s2 1 s3 1 -m 2
bcadd result s1 0 s2 1 s3 1 -m 2
bcremoveint result

donly result
fit

checkprops result -s 4494.64

